        <div class="content-sizer">
            <div class="features-container">
                <div class="feature-card feature-large">
                    <div class="category-label">Accelerate your card product</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Expedite the security and compliance requirements of launching a card
                        product
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-description">Improve your card's time-to-market from months to days, by using
                        Evervault to tokenize cards from the issuer of your choice, store card data with minimal PCI
                        compliance impact, and even reveal the raw card numbers to users.
                    </div>
                    <div class="learn-more">Learn more</div>
                    <div class="illustration-area">
                        <div class="card-stack">
                            <div class="card"></div>
                            <div class="card"></div>
                            <div class="card"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card feature-medium">
                    <div class="illustration-area">
                        <div class="partner-logos">
                            <div class="logo">
                                <img src="path/to/logo1.svg" alt="Partner Logo">
                            </div>
                            <div class="logo">
                                <img src="path/to/logo2.svg" alt="Partner Logo">
                            </div>
                            <div class="logo">
                                <img src="path/to/logo3.svg" alt="Partner Logo">
                            </div>
                            <div class="logo">
                                <img src="path/to/logo4.svg" alt="Partner Logo">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="category-label">Optimize payment performance</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Improve payment costs & global coverage with a multi-processor payment
                        setup
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-description">Avoid payment processor vendor lock-in, optimize payment costs and
                        acceptance rates by selectively routing payments to different payment processors.
                    </div>
                    <div class="learn-more">Learn more</div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card feature-medium">
                    <div class="category-label">Build complex card sharing workflows</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Share card data securely while keeping compliance scope to a minimum
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-description">Evervault gives you flexible, compliant products for sharing card
                        data with third-parties. For example, booking aggregators and platforms can compliantly forward
                        card data to their partners for storing or processing.
                    </div>
                    <div class="learn-more">Learn more</div>
                    <div class="illustration-area">
                        <div class="card-proxy">
                            <!-- Add card proxy illustration here -->
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card feature-large">
                    <div class="illustration-area">
                        <div class="security-dial"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="category-label">Computing for highly sensitive payment operations</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Easily prove to enterprise customers that their data is handled with
                        maximum security
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-description">Evervault makes it easy for developers to run sensitive payment
                        workloads in highly-constrained compute environments using secure enclaves.
                    </div>
                    <div class="learn-more">Learn more</div>
                </div>
